sentence: what are the major cities in the state of california ?
sentence-with-vars: what are the major cities in the state of state0 ?
sql: select city.city_name from city where city.population > 150000 and city.state_name = ' california ' ;
sql-with-vars: select city.city_name from city where city.population > number0 and city.state_name = ' state0 ' ;
